## 7. How to Run
```bash
# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run server
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

- Open `http://127.0.0.1:8000/` â†’ Neat HTML welcome page
- Open `http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs` â†’ Swagger UI
- Open `http://127.0.0.1:8000/redoc` â†’ ReDoc

---

## 8. Testing Workflow
1. Register a patient (`POST /patients/`).
2. Log vitals for that patient (`POST /vitals/`).
3. Retrieve patient info (`GET /patients/{id}`).
4. Retrieve vitals (`GET /vitals/{id}`).
5. Use SQL queries to confirm data persistence.
